# --- EXCEPTIONS ---
# Force-include the DLL needed for the project to run
!bin/freeglut.dll
!freeglut.dll

# Force-include the built executable so the 'final build' goes through
!bin/x64/OpenGL.exe
!x64/Release/OpenGL.exe